OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Parents to 'risk    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftruancy fines' if school   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcases rise                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some parents have said they are willing
OL,6, to take their children out of class and
OL,7, risk truancy fines if Covid cases rise 
OL,8, now pupils are back in schools.        
OL,10,FThe reintroduction of truancy fines for
OL,11,Fparents who repeatedly keep their      
OL,12,Fchildren off school is being reviewed  
OL,13,Fafter it was suspended during Covid.   
OL,15,FWelsh government guidelines currently  
OL,16,Fstate pupils can attend school if      
OL,17,Fsomeone they live with has Covid-19.   
OL,19,FThe government said some measures were 
OL,20,Fremoved due to the Covid jab rollout.  
